[normal]whose normal place of residence was 
[normal]Palest
[normal]ine
[normal] between June 1946 and May 1948, [and] who lost both their homes and means of livelihood as a result of 
[normal]the 1948 Arab-Israeli conflict.” 
[normal]In fact, fewer than 10
[normal] percent of today’s UNRWA-classified refugees were born before 1948
[normal].
