[normal]ny person who, not being Jewish, possessed Palestinian nationality before 15 May 1948 and was a regular resident in the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan between 20 Dece
[normal]mber 1949 and 16 February 1954.” In addition, the law states: “
[normal]The childr
[normal]en of a Jordanian man shall be Jordanian wherever they are born.
[normal]”
[normal] Yet a great grandchild of a Jordanian 
[normal]citizen
